<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= subject %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;

            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;

            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;

        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: left;
        }

        thead {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .signature {
            font-weight: bold;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .button-container {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .button {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            /* Adjust padding for better spacing */
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            flex: 1;
            /* Allows buttons to take equal space */
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 100px;
            margin: 5px;
            /* Ensures buttons don't shrink too much */
        }

        .approve-btn {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        .reject-btn {
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }

        /* Ensure buttons take full width on smaller screens */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .button {
                flex: none;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <p>Hi User,</p>
    <p>Quote no request got rejected. The reason for rejection is mentioned below.</p>
    <p>Kindly fix and request again.</p>
   
    <h3><%= reason %></h3>

    <p>This is an auto generated mail. Please do not reply.</p>

    <p class="signature">Thanks & Regards!</p>

    <p>
        <%= senderName %>
    </p>
    <p>Acero Building Systems</p>
</body>

</html>